{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make convicted murdered ineligible for compassionate release",
        "additional_details": "They took a life away and are serving a life sentence. Why should their life ending mean they can be released from their sentence and give them freedom to die in the outside world, when their victims didn\u2019t get this privilege?",
        "background": "Remove the rights of convicted murderers applying for compassionate release, which is often granted when they are on the end of life pathway. They shouldn\u2019t be eligible for compassionate release for it they\u2019re serving a sentence for taking a life.",
